namedLocations.description: A letterhead is the heading at the top of a sheet of letter paper (stationery). That heading usually consists of a name and an address, and a logo or corporate design, and sometimes a background pattern. The term "letterhead" is often used to refer to the whole sheet imprinted with such a heading.

namedLocations.description: A ZIP Code is a postal code used by the United States Postal Service (USPS) in a system it introduced in 1963. The term ZIP is an acronym for Zone Improvement Plan; it was chosen to suggest that the mail travels more efficiently and quickly (zipping along) when senders use the code in the postal address. The basic format consists of five digits. An extended ZIP+4 code was introduced in 1983 which includes the five digits of the ZIP Code, followed by a hyphen and four additional digits that reference a more specific location.

transcript.text: Good morning.
Today we will see how to have a batch on your product on which will display on the home page as well as it can be displayed on the product listing page.
So I am talking about this kind of batch that is new.
You can have a batch or a promotional offer.
You can give a 50% discount promotional offer on this product or something like that.
You can create a batch that can attract your customers.
Now let us take an example of creating a badge on this product.
So for that you need to go and select this product standard business card.
Click on action, click on Settings and on the right hand side you have other settings in which there is an option called Enable promotional text on the title.
Click on Yes and enter the title that you want.
For example, let us take festive offer 50% discount.
And here are the badges different kind of badges that are badges that are available over here.
You can select the one you like the most.
And please also note and remember that the badges depends upon the theme that you have on your website.
Few some of the badge may not support the theme or theme may not support particular batch.
So in that case you just replace the batch.
Let us click take an example of cross label or let us take the ribbon as the batch.
It will display on the front store as well as on the product page.
Click on save and go from the front store and refresh the page.
Now here you have the same way you can have it on product listing as well.
Here it is when you click, when you select a particular product.
For example, if you select this one and you go in here, here also you will find this batch or this promotional offer coming on to this product.
So this way you can set the batch for a particular product the way you want to promote it.
Thank you, have a nice day.
Bye bye.
